                <span class="riva-msg-avatar">🦢</span>
                <div class="riva-msg-bubble">Hey@(ViewBag.UserName != null ? " " + ViewBag.UserName : " there")! 👋 I'm <strong>Yenkah</strong>, your AI assistant on MakauTech. Ask me anything — from Sibu tourism to tech, science, or just a fun chat! Tap 🔊 to hear my voice.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
